Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Something this small but fancy \Nis certain to become an eye-catcher!{unsure what he means, lit: itsy-bitsy successful guy - if I do it, everyone will be surprised}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!{tadaima}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how to knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing that damn special!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding things not polite.{/you shouldnt conceal it} \NLet me see!{/tell me}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, will you?{dunno what he means, most likely don't you know when to stop}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of being mean, \Nyou could just show me!{unsure what's sou iwazu ni, most likely "without saying that"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She-ki-ret!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Balls-up!\NStill raw inside!{/Turning them over too soon!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Start over once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the progress you've made.{unsure which suji it is because it apparently has a ton of meanings, most likely aptitude; talent}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru,{unsure this is what taru means as they don't seem to be that familiar and I wouldn't expect him to call taru by name} we ain't eating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it!{finished would fit here better, but this way it's not the same phrase taru used when he learned to make takoyaki}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little rough{/weird/odd} here and there, \Nbut still a fairly good job, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I try, I can do anything, too!{unsure what he means, I suspect he compares humself to iyona whom he had previously attributed with "can do anything if she makes an effort"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Just gotta find a transparent case \Nthat fits it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I so want to find out what Honmaru's present is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't stand anymore!{/no patience left}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(360,435,360,500,1260,1300)}Fell apart!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(360,20,360,435,0,270)}Taru... You broke it!{unsure, maybe he is asking it}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, what now, what now?{doshio /what to do}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was losing my goddamn sleep{unsure it's nenaide} making it!{ with all my might}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is my tree! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've crossed the line... {/how could you}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Christmas is not the time \Nto make enemies.{/to get mad at each other/you shouldn't get angry about christmas}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what? Say what? Say what? \NIt's not your present that just got smashed!{/what what what? but what about the present I made}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to bring tomorrow?\NThere's no time to make a new one!{/that was my only option for taking tomorrow, if I start now, I can't make it in time}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas, what kind of day is that?{it seems as though she is asking because she never knew what's christmas, but that cant be true as we've seen her explaining he shouldn't get mad so im confused}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of day, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With "Jingle Bells" playing, \Ndad and mom put presents in the socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And we eat one big cake...{/have a feast with ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you at least remember \Nwhose birthday is on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Jesus Christ's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo. {/Ping-pong.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, even if it's his birthday, \Nhow is it related to making enemies?{/why are you saying I shouldn't get angry}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On Christmas, one should avoid \Narguing or quarreling with others.{/getting angry or fighting is a no-go}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the time for getting along.{/instead, start ... will you}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make up for your tree, somehow. \NBut you should forgive Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind it. \NJust wait here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is that huge fir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just something fancy \NI found on a mountain side.{/near mt}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's hurry up and decorate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, I help too! \NLet's do{ it}, let's do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't bring along a thing this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, let's do, let's do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it, did it splendidly{dunno what's that haato}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice we decorated it, \Nbut how am I supposed to bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all fine if you shrink it with magic!{/you can make it small}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This miniature's a lot more elaborate!{/detailed}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This would do perfectly for tomorrow's Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, remember that sister Ria's magic \Nwears off in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll make an inscription "big enough" \Nfor anyone to understand.{this might or might not be a pun: clearly he means "I'll write 'becomes big' in terms clear enough for anyone' but he puts it the strange way - write big}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine if I'm lucky enough \Nto have Iyona-chan receive this tree!{/it would be good if this tree falls on iyona}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One, and a-two, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A sleigh is like the wind, \Ndashing through the snow{走れそりよ 風のように}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:35.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fade(1800,0)\c&H483751&\3c&HADA8A8&}Merry {\c&H213925&}Christmas {\c&H45294B&}1990
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how light can it be,\Nlook how fast can it go!{雪の中を 軽く 早く}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Our laughter is the seed,{笑い声を 雪にまけば}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,sow it in the snow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So buds of glitter and delight \Nsprout up before you know!{明るいひかりの 花になるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:53.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,Jingle bells, jingle bells \NBells keep on jingling {鈴が鳴る}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting Iyona-chan's present would be nice, too...{it's 来る from manga and im unsure what is it, maybe i hope iyona's present comes my way when the song stops}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:58.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,Light is dancing in circles \Nwhile the bells are marking rhythm \N{鈴のリズムに ひかりの輪が 舞う}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:03.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,Jingle bells, jingle bells \NBells keep on jingling {鈴が鳴る}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:08.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,Through the forests, through the groves \Nyou can hear them echoing{森に林に 響きながら}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My present is nearing Iyona-chan!{/going to ...'s place}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OH MY GOD!\NWhy did it have to end up in Jabao's claws?{/why does it have to go to someone like jabao}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, let's open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona! My tasty present! Eat it, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry up and bite!{/eat}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that at old lad's{added} takoyaki shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ultimate takoyaki!{/the best?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, eating Taru-chan's takoyaki \N makes me suddenly oh-so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This here is one badass tree!{/amazing}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's precise down to the smallest details!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It even has working lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world could have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that I would be the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honmaru did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine craftsmanship, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But now this tree is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even those begging me with their "Please let me see it," \Nwill get to actually see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see it, Jabao-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you can look at it all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This douche!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is my tree bringing closer \NIyona-chan and Jabao instead?!{lit is "why/what jabao and yona" - methinks he means why does iyona have to ask jabao to see it}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a toy Santa-san!{/doll of}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From Iyona!{/it's Iyona's}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lucky, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's this thing I got -\Na botched clay toad that Jabao pasted together.{/compared to mine clumsy ...} Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see it, Jabao-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao, that prick!...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas is not the time to make enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you can have my present, too.{/I will lend you this} Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. One should not \Nhold any grudges on Christmas.{/is not the time to get angry}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious indeed!{hope its oishisou}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! When it's actually Christmas eve,{I hope this is what he means by "true christmas"} \NI'll give Iyona-chan another hand-made present!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A brooch, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Think I can make it in time?{/if I hurry, it seems I'll be able to make it in time}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, sounds great! \NMake Iyona happy!{unsure what he means, maybe just that she is already happy}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't spill it to anyone else!{/but it's a secret to ... - hope its minna}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru busy all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do.{/a bit bored}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna-wanna-wanna! \NSanta Claus, give-give-give! Lemme touch it! {/I had no idea I'll get to see Santa Claus so soon!} {guess, first part sounds a bit like ore ha sugu de - might be some name of the mall or something, asogu? no clue what is sounashite either, maybe he says "people shouldn't be seeing you so soon"} {13:17　ほし！ほし！ほし！サンタクロース。生み出す触らしてくれれれ \Naudio is garbled so not 100% sure. This is my best attempt at deciphering the dialogue. - AU}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this at once, or I'm handing you over to the police!{/if you don't calm down I'll call the police}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know when to stop, you brat?!{/not pissing off are you}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:57.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.2\b1\c&H483AB2&\3c&HC1BCCA&}Reminder: {\c&H33302C&}in 10 days, it grows {\fscx200}mighty{\fscx100} big, fella!{注意：１０日たったらでかくなるよーん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't give it to you during the school party.{unsure, lit is "if in school, without giving it" - maybe he means "I can't hand it over in school [with everyone looking]" or smt}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you schmuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree was a trap!{lit: you put a trick/device/handywork into the tree}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your freaking tree, \Nmom gave me the hardest beating ever!{/you made this tree to make mom beat me didnt you}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you didn't even try to read the inscription!{/you didn't read it properly did you}\NIt said "big again after ten days" pretty damn clearly!{/that's why I wrote ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what?{/what'd you sya}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be fighting, both of you! \NAfter all, it's Christmas eve!{/today is ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it freaking matter?{/so what}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ's birthday? Christ's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any chump by that name!{/don't know nothing of the kind}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell does Christ know about it?{/what is .../what does it have to do with ...}
